1
00:00:01,585 --> 00:00:04,546
[QUEEN KANE] <i>I won't die for this
city. This city will die for me.</i>

2
00:00:05,797 --> 00:00:07,048
[SHOUTS]

3
00:00:07,049 --> 00:00:09,092
[SCREAMS] Nyrie!

4
00:00:09,593 --> 00:00:11,093
[CUTTER] <i>What have you brought me?</i>

5
00:00:11,094 --> 00:00:14,347
I will speak to you. You've
made a mistake... [GRUNTS]

6
00:00:14,348 --> 00:00:17,226
I wonder who you might
be to make such a claim.

7
00:00:17,835 --> 00:00:20,102
[BABA VOSS] <i>Opayol. They're
the ones who took our things.</i>

8
00:00:20,103 --> 00:00:22,355
[HANIWA] <i>There's no one down
there. It looks deserted.</i>

9
00:00:22,356 --> 00:00:24,899
[MEN GROWLING, GRUNTING]

10
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:26,984
Stop! Feel! His chest.

11
00:00:26,985 --> 00:00:28,486
[RAGGED BREATH] He can see.

12
00:00:28,487 --> 00:00:30,905
Boots is Jerlamarel's son. Our brother.

13
00:00:30,906 --> 00:00:32,030
Where's Mama? What happened?

14
00:00:32,031 --> 00:00:33,157
They took her?

15
00:00:33,158 --> 00:00:35,618
No, she let go of my hand.

16
00:00:35,619 --> 00:00:36,620
Tamacti Jun!

17
00:00:37,412 --> 00:00:38,746
[JINGLES]

18
00:00:38,747 --> 00:00:40,331
Princess Maghra...

